latestPosts.caption:
To celebrate 15 Years of Mike’s Hot Honey we commissioned Philadelphia-based artist Hawk Krall to illustrate our 15th Anniversary poster and pizza box.

The poster and box pay tribute to our pizza community and the folks who have made up the backbone of our brand since day one. 

Both the poster and box will soon be available in limited quantities. 

🖼️ @hkrall 
📷 @davefotogram
